title: 032 - Have You Heard Of ShahhhkWheels?
description: On today's show, the guys discuss a wild issue at Digs' neighbors house, the neighbors at the new Pub hating Connor and wanting nothing to do with him, potential asteroids hitting the earth, Harrison Ford doing whatever the hell he wants in an airplane, and some more of the things the guys have been watching during quarantine. As always, stay safe, have a great weekend, and enjoy.
